	Fully covered subdomains:

		- assets1
		- assets2
		- download
		- framegrabs
		- mtoza
		- resources
		- static	(â†’ s3.amazonaws.com)
		- view


	Insecure cookies are set for these domains:

		- view.vzaar.com

